  <h3>Designs</h3>

	<p>Way back in 2016 I was browsing online programs to find an online course of study that might interest me. I hit the jackpot when I found the University of Missouri’s learning technologies and design EdS program. At the time I had no idea that an EdS degree existed, but this program allowed me to advance beyond a master’s degree and learn about things that I enjoy&mdash;design and instructional theories.  I found the courses to be very hands-on whereas the courses in my master’s program were mostly theoretical.</p>
	

	
	
